**Input:**

```shell
db.<collection>.createSearchIndex(
  "default",
  {
    "mappings": {
      "dynamic": true|false,
      "fields": {
        "<field-name>": {
          "type": "document",
          "dynamic": true|false | {
            "typeSet": "<typeSet-name>"
          },
          "fields": {
            "<sub-field-name>": {
              <field-mapping-definition>
            },
            ...
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "typeSets": [
      {
        "name": "<typeSet-name>",
        "types": [
          {
            "type": "<field-type>",
            ...
          },
          ...
        ]
      },
      ...
    ]
  }
)
```

**Output:**

```
default
```

